item.title: David, the Failed Intercessor on Mount Zion
item.description: The Mountain E6 — In 2 Samuel, David is crowned king of a unified Israel, and after choosing Jerusalem as his capital city, he brings the ark of the covenant to Mount Zion. It seems like things are going great—a priestly king has unified the tribes and all of Israel’s enemies are subdued! But it doesn’t last. After committing adultery and murder, David also foolishly calls for a census of his army (which according to the Law, no Israelite leader was supposed to do). And things just get worse... item.title: The Proud Tree Fairy Tale for Kids & Teens
item.description:
Welcome to the SweetDream bedtime podcast for kids. With a mix of timeless fairy tales and original stories join us every night for a touch of bedtime magic as our episodes are filled with extraordinary adventures, magical realms, and lovable characters that will send your child to sleep. So get cozy, close your eyes, and let your imagination wander as we dive into a world of bedtime wonders. Sweet Dreams!!!
